In [ ]:
train_df = df2.iloc[:-1]
test_row = df2.iloc[-1]  # [200]
train_df
test_row

closest_dist = 9999999
closest_label = None
for i in range(len(train_df)):
    train_row = train_df.iloc[i]
    # dist = (train_row.feature1 - test_row.feature1) ** 2 + (train_row.feature2 - test_row.feature2) ** 2
    dist = abs(train_row.feature1 - test_row.feature1) + abs(train_row.feature2 - test_row.feature2)
    if dist < closest_dist:
        closest_dist = dist
        # closest_label = (i >= 100) * 1
        if i >= 100:
            closest_label = 1
        else:
            closest_label = 0

print('Closest distance:', np.sqrt(closest_dist))
print('Predicted label:', closest_label)

Closest distance: 0.21739743901887407
Predicted label: 1
